### Mathematical References

#### Ramanujan's Universal Quadratic Forms
- Based on work by Srinivasa Ramanujan (1917)
- "On the expression of numbers in the form ax²+by²+cz²+du²"
- Public domain mathematical knowledge

#### Hilbert Space Theory
- Based on work by David Hilbert (1900)
- "Mathematical Problems - Foundations of Geometry"
- Public domain mathematical knowledge

#### Fano Plane Structure
- Based on work by Gino Fano (1892)
- Finite projective plane of order 2
- Public domain mathematical knowledge

